{"tid":1819934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懇請大家一定要持續去黃店","createTime":"2020-01-11T08:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-11T17:11:07.000Z","uid":37528,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dc803826ee5df929b08564ede3522300f14ecf","tid":1819934,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"唔好好似支那咁短視，見到短時間無乜成果就放棄<br />\n我地見到元氣執，富臨執，吉野家執果陣好鼓舞，正正就係因為我地杯葛呢堆藍店，我地每個有參與杯葛既人都有功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有，支那睇死我地黃色經濟圈會失敗，因為我地激進深黃消費力好疲弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想講既係，大把深黃和理非係上曬岸有錢有樓<br />\n而可能學生未出黎做野賺錢，當佢地畢業後又可以繼續擴闊黃色經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n總之我地夠團結夠齊心，keep著呢個form再做好d整合黃色經濟，一定可以成功<br />\n<br />\n黃店，外國網購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有減少用八達通，由買野做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fc0357a4fee68b3d010a4949a271ff150104c7","tid":1819934,"uid":340189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人團結<br />\n香港人反抗<br />\n香港人堅持</strong></span>"},{"pid":"fc08b48e82a22a258ccad7ffe484a811a4a29325","tid":1819934,"uid":338125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:41:41.000Z","msg":"依家未到五點<br />\n已經食左三間黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650691d33766a2576c1f4bf3f5a083f5775edbb8","tid":1819934,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:57:43.000Z","msg":"m記咪黃店 個logo黃色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444738c1657b3be561e2ecf0c0f166d3bf52d825","tid":1819934,"uid":76103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該繼續罷藍店"},{"pid":"c56e38c3f91e0579cdb947458ffae30a950e57bf","tid":1819934,"uid":249705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f48b3516bc79d301035d918bd2e91358f2293f90","tid":1819934,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T15:35:55.000Z","msg":"認同,所以唔該幫手入去推:<br />\n屌你! 黃色經濟圈根本影響唔到d資源分配!<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過無所謂<br />\n因為學波蘭人將抗爭融入生活先係目的</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">明明好成功,我哋錯咗重點啫,調整心態就得</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1820242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1820242</a>"},{"pid":"0cd5d8aef332659d4ee6687e52291c0cf3dd4eb3","tid":1819934,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"附近冇黃店 食大快活食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時食下mos burger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e4a593bc087eb827fb59d8abdedac6d05b6489","tid":1819934,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cd5d8aef332659d4ee6687e52291c0cf3dd4eb3","tid":1819934,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:43:17.000Z","msg":"附近冇黃店 食大快活食到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時食下mos burger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T17:11:07.000Z","msg":"你住邊區？"}]}